column2: SELECT TOP # s.z as z_spec, p.objid, p.dered_g, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_r, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cs as combined_spiral   FROM Galaxy as p     JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid     JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  WHERE s.z between # and # and zns.p_el > #
